    <h2 class="sect-title">About Coach Hill</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">The community is surrounded by the Old Banff Coach Road, the 69th Street the Bow Trail and the Sarcee Trail on the north, west, south and east respectively.</p>

            <p class="par-lg">Coach Hill homes for sale include a wide range of housing facilities including detached homes, condominiums and townhouses.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">Coach hill condos, single family homes and townhomes have been renovated from time to time and are designed strategically with well structured landscaping.</p>
